Sentencas: A new composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cells based on Ca3Co4O9 (C349) and PrOx was synthesized using a novel solution blow spinning (SBS) process.
Titulo: Electrochemical assessment of novel misfit Ca-cobaltite-based composite SOFC cathodes synthesized by solution blow spinning

Sentencas: It is demonstrated that the presence of PrOx in this cathode permits a remarkable decrease in total polarisation resistance, by 15 times, mainly due to improvements in charge transfer and surface exchange processes.
Titulo: Electrochemical assessment of novel misfit Ca-cobaltite-based composite SOFC cathodes synthesized by solution blow spinning
